{"_id":"a2WFwJYHnygMeokf","name":"[T4c] Collapsed Tomb","content":"<p>This tomb has partially collapsed into the upper reaches of Murrie’s Cave, allowing access to that area. The bier, along with the remains and items resting on it, has fallen through into the caves.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qrblv55YbGxLkaKf":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":600000},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.QnxsM2haEwiqDOMx","hash":"8952704cf69fffb075621c4f02a5ffd56517fffe"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.hm-loc-tbb.journals.glDlIr1y6jr0VORa"},"cf":{"id":"temp_slr7zci5iw","path":"Three Brothers Barrow#/CF_SEP/Tomb","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"mCXI63y3yIvzrg3S","name":"[C2] Pool","content":"<p>Downstream of the entrance, the water forms a small pool before flowing out through a submerged passage. Murrie will be found here, either unconscious or dead (GM discretion). Regardless of his status when the PCs discover him, it’s clear that he was badly injured by the fall: he has a broken leg and several cracked ribs, as well as numerous cuts, scrapes, and bruises. If he is still alive, he will be incapable of providing much assistance to the PCs.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qrblv55YbGxLkaKf":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":400000},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.hm-loc-tbb.journals.KMprJKvFxjd4usaQ"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.0XiaLKbON5HtKuB3","hash":"395df17020209eedbffd51151d73daa54b424bb6"},"cf":{"id":"temp_20qazfcekn","path":"Three Brothers Barrow#/CF_SEP/Murrie's Cave","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"mjgllaZy9Ydd2lJ8","name":"[T1] Sealed Entrance","content":"<p>The hillside entrance to the barrow is covered over with earth and grass and has lain undetected for centuries.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qrblv55YbGxLkaKf":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":200000},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.U12BgV41Ow90AoLO","hash":"5487238cc0d75286726f3c49adfba9d0eb78f99f"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.hm-loc-tbb.journals.yorIzSVpfQTb9vxU"},"cf":{"id":"temp_slr7zci5iw","path":"Three Brothers Barrow#/CF_SEP/Tomb","color":"#000000"}}}
