{"_id":"oVNtKDxm0asyJFcj","name":"[1] The Pasture","content":"<p>Three Brothers Barrow is located in an area of hilly pastures. The GM can locate it on any civilized manor that is suitable for raising sheep. Ideally, the pasture should be a short distance from the village and manor house, near enough that help can be summoned if needed but too far to simply shout for it.</p>\n<p>The pasture can be reached by a local road or trail, but to reach the site of the barrow itself involves trekking several hundred yards up a slope. Because of the recent rains, the conditions will be wet and mud may be a hindrance in places. The wet, muddy conditions may justify one or more tests of Agility if PCs are moving quickly, such as if trying to keep up with an anxious sheepdog.</p>\n<p>Visibility in the pasture may be limited by the weather conditions. On a clear day, however, the two hilltops offer a good vantage point to see much of the manor lands, especially to the southwest of the barrow.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qrblv55YbGxLkaKf":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":200000},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.hm-loc-tbb.journals.ci855Na3hWTfebqs"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.TB4Tx4OHVc86N8zI","hash":"a49f8060b500d3260c55d734506503243e822446"},"cf":{"id":"temp_26dq2y78fg8","path":"Three Brothers Barrow#/CF_SEP/Pasture","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"q0Cdjo0cVdLV8clt","name":"[C5] Tomb Collapse","content":"<p>At the top of the slope, a section of the tunnel ceiling has collapsed, revealing an opening that is low enough to be easily accessed. This is how the PCs will be able to enter the Three Brothers Barrow.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qrblv55YbGxLkaKf":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":1000000},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.hm-loc-tbb.journals.BOMO14piadt42aFG"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.RifE6X46Tln9DaYy","hash":"de5cb6b36b50057e38595633b6d66138f64a7999"},"cf":{"id":"temp_20qazfcekn","path":"Three Brothers Barrow#/CF_SEP/Murrie's Cave","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"rbviCI66eoIK93h9","name":"[T4a] Wealthy Warrior","content":"<p>This tomb holds the remains of a wealthy Jarin warrior. A silver brooch (10 oz. with gold inlay in the form of a stag’s head) rests on the skeletal chest of the dead warrior.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qrblv55YbGxLkaKf":3},"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":200000},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.BS2HBxvycmKSG3L6","hash":"201f2393ed74abee2ca086c335e046926c80a0e4"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.hm-loc-tbb.journals.uMAi08MJQrTjERWe"},"cf":{"id":"temp_slr7zci5iw","path":"Three Brothers Barrow#/CF_SEP/Tomb","color":"#000000"}}}
